::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer nods. "Ok, let's go," he says, turning around, his eyes glancing 
across a computer panel, displaying scanner reports. He frowns, walking 
toward it. It reported gunfire and a concentration of bots near the Predacon 
cave.

"Hey," he says, turning around, "There's a battle at the Pred cave, maybe we 
should join in!"
